      "message": "[Major] Line 65: editedWidth is now always 0, but TextMessageDelegate still uses rootDelegate.editedWidth in the right margin calculation. For non-big outgoing messages this removes the reserved space for the edited/modified indicator and timestamp/action text can overlap or be clipped. Either remove the margin dependency completely if the indicator is no longer inline, or bind editedWidth to the new editedRow width.\n```suggestion\nproperty real editedWidth: editedRow.visible ? editedRow.implicitWidth + 10 : 0\n```",
