      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 66: showOriginal is only reset when Id changes. In virtualized delegates, Body/OriginalBody/ParsedOriginalBody can change for the same item after edits, plugin updates, or model refreshes, leaving the UI showing an original body that no longer matches the current message state. Reset or validate the toggle when the overwrite inputs change.\n```suggestion\nonIdChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\nonOriginalBodyChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\nonBodyChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\n```",
      "revId": "d2a46da900e5244b72ba1748ed9e3f78d8afcbb3",
