      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 411: The asynchronous original-message parse result is applied to whatever conversation is selected when parsing finishes. If the user switches conversations while the worker is running, this can update the wrong MessageListModel or silently fail if the message id does not exist there. Pass the conversation/account id through the parse request, or look up the interaction by a stable conversation id captured at request time instead of using get_selectedConvUid() in the completion slot.",
